  <!-- ═══════ PART 3: EXISTING LANDSCAPE ═══════ -->
  <section class="page-section">
    <div class="section-eyebrow reveal">Part Three</div>
    <h2 class="section-heading reveal">The Existing Font Landscape.</h2>
    <p class="section-sub reveal" style="margin-bottom:2.5rem;">
      What exists, what's missing, and why nothing currently available solves the problem.
    </p>

    <div class="table-wrap reveal">
